@node distri "Distribution"

  5. DISTRIBUTION
  ---------------

  As IconUpdate specifically processes MagicWB-Icons and was programmed for
  the use with MagicWB it should only be used if converting an old icon to
  a MagicWB-Icon.

  Therefore it is only allowed to be distributed in conjunction with MagicWB!

@endnode
